sentence: beulah j. huggins age 85, of west palm beach, florida.
passed away quietly on tuesday, june 9, 2015 at west palm hospital following an extended illness.
huggins was a homemaker privately for many years.

she leaves to mourn her passing her loving and devoted children; kelvin c. (nadine) blount, of miami gardens, fl.; brenda lee, of royal palm beach, fl. and karen (bobby) cowan, of west palm beach, fl.
eight grandchildren, nine great-grandchildren and a host of many other relatives and sorrowing friends.
homegoing services will be held saturday, june 13, 2015 at 10:00 a. m. at timothy e. kitchens funeral home chapel.
friends may call on friday, june 12, 2015 from 6 - 8 p. m. at the chapel mentioned above.
